---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { ShieldCheck } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="CODE:LIFE Tools について"
  description="CODE:LIFE Toolsの概要・特徴・技術スタック・運営者情報。完全クライアントサイド処理の日本語業務特化Webツール集。"
  path="/about"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[960px] px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-primary"><ShieldCheck className="h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12" /></span>
        <span>CODE:LIFE Tools</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium">
        仕事で安心して使える、高速・軽量なWebツール集
      </p>

      <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-safety/30 bg-safety/5 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-safety font-medium">
        <ShieldCheck className="h-4 w-4" />
        完全クライアントサイド処理で機密データも安心
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">3つの特徴</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="mb-4"><ShieldCheck className="h-10 w-10" /></div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">完全クライアントサイド処理</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-2 text-left w-full list-disc pl-5">
            <li>すべてのデータ処理はブラウザ内で完結</li>
            <li>サーバーへのデータ送信は一切なし</li>
            <li>ソースコードはGitHubで公開し透明性を確保</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🇯🇵</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">日本語業務に特化</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-2 text-left w-full list-disc pl-5">
            <li>全角半角変換、Shift-JISバイト数など日本固有の機能</li>
            <li>UI・エラーメッセージすべて自然な日本語</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">高速・軽量</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-2 text-left w-full list-disc pl-5">
            <li>サーバー通信なしのリアルタイム処理</li>
            <li>Astroによる最適化された静的サイト</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <!-- Tech Stack Section -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">技術スタック</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-border bg-muted/50 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">Astro</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-border bg-muted/50 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">React</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-border bg-muted/50 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">shadcn/ui</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-border bg-muted/50 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">Tailwind CSS</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-border bg-muted/50 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold">Cloudflare Pages</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          本サイトはオープンソースプロジェクトです。ソースコードは<a href="https://github.com/maru0014/tools-codelife-cafe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline font-medium">GitHubリポジトリ</a>で公開しています。
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Operator & Contact Section -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">運営者</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="font-semibold w-20">運営:</span>
              <span>marumo</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="font-semibold w-20">サイト:</span>
              <a href="https://codelife.cafe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">CODE:LIFE (codelife.cafe)</a>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="font-semibold w-20">GitHub:</span>
              <a href="https://github.com/maru0014" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">github.com/maru0014</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">お問い合わせ・フィードバック</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            機能リクエストやバグ報告は大歓迎です。<br />
            以下のGitHub Issuesよりお気軽にご連絡ください。
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/maru0014/tools-codelife-cafe/issues"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 px-4 py-2"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="mr-2"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"></path></svg>
            GitHub Issues を開く
          </a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
